text: Jason Michael Palmer (born December 1, 1971) is an American politician, entrepreneur and impact investor. He was a candidate in the 2024 Democratic Party presidential primaries. On March 5, 2024, Palmer defeated incumbent president Joe Biden in the by a vote of 51 to 40. ==References== Category:21st-century American politicians Category:1971 births Category:2024 United States presidential candidates Category:Businesspeople from Maryland Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Maryland
